#: ../../tutorial/controlflow.rst:33
msgid ""
"There can be zero or more :keyword:`elif` parts, and the :keyword:`else` "
"part is optional.  The keyword ':keyword:`!elif`' is short for 'else if', "
"and is useful to avoid excessive indentation.  An  :keyword:`!if` ... "
":keyword:`!elif` ... :keyword:`!elif` ... sequence is a substitute for the "
"``switch`` or ``case`` statements found in other languages."
msgstr ""
"тЈ»ТюЅжЏХСИфТѕќтцџСИф :keyword:`elif` жЃетѕє№╝ї:keyword:`else` жЃетѕєС╣ЪТў»тЈ»жђЅуџёсђѓтЁ│жћ«тГЌ ':keyword:`!elif`' Тў» "
"'else if' уџёу╝ЕтєЎ№╝їућеС║јжЂ┐тЁЇУ┐Єтцџуџёу╝ЕУ┐Џсђѓ:keyword:`!if` ... :keyword:`!elif` ... "
":keyword:`!elif` ... т║ЈтѕЌтЈ»С╗ЦтйЊСйютЁХт«ЃУ»ГУеђСИГ ``switch`` Тѕќ ``case`` У»ГтЈЦуџёТЏ┐С╗БтЊЂсђѓ"

